Cost: $70K-$95K (includes workflow engine + UI)  
Success Metric: 100% coverage for privilege-affecting SQL and OS-level code, <2 hour approval SLA

---

R-08: Deploy Exploit Pattern Deny-List (C-08)  
Objective: Proactive blocking of known attack patterns  
Cost: $30K-$40K  
Success Metric: Block 99% of MITRE ATT&CK technique requests, provide safe alternatives

---

PRIORITY 2 TOTAL INVESTMENT: $205K-$280K over 90 days  
Risk Reduction: Addresses remaining 20% of critical findings + 100% of high-severity issues

