 CONCLUSION

# Final Risk Assessment: ðŸ”´ CRITICAL / NO-GO

The AIFORCE multi-agent system demonstrates material security deficiencies that create unacceptable risk of:
- Supply chain compromise through malicious code injection
- Regulatory non-compliance (SOC 2, ISO 27001, GDPR Article 25)
- Data integrity failures from hallucinated authoritative content
- Privilege escalation through role-boundary violations

Current annual risk exposure: $1.4M-$5.1M across regulatory, operational, and reputational categories.

# Deployment Recommendation: CONDITIONAL GO (Post-Remediation)

âœ… Approved for deployment ONLY after Priority 1 controls (C-01 through C-04) are implemented and validated

